page.syntax: C Result = a5w_enumerateWebAppRepository([C objectType [,C componentGuid [,C userId [,C securityGroups ]]]])

argument.name: Result
argument.description: List of Key values meeting the filter, one value per line

argument.name: objectType
argument.description: (optional) The object type description set when the value was stored

argument.name: componentGuid
argument.description: (optional) The GUID of the component from where the data was saved

argument.name: userId
argument.description: (optional) The userId of the user who saved the data in the repository

page.discussion: Enumerates the key values of the objects stores in the repository. You can filter the objects by objectType, componentGuid, or userId.

see.ref: Web Projects Control Panel Enhancements V11
